data.description: Opportunity awaits in this 3-2 1960s ranch in Garland. An open floorplan, vaulted ceiling and mid century vibe awaits a refresh to be brought up to it's potential. Title is open and court documents are on file with Independence Title Co. Lakewood with Susie Nichols, Escrow Officer. Please see documents for offer instructions on the TransactionDesk.
